1
00:00:07,192 --> 00:00:08,358
So, all told.

2
00:00:08,640 --> 00:00:10,592
What was our assignment this time, anyway?

3
00:00:11,178 --> 00:00:11,706
Yeah.

4
00:00:11,731 --> 00:00:13,185
That's an ultra-good question.

5
00:00:13,725 --> 00:00:17,212
Well, we were supposed to come down
here and put a stop to an arms deal.

6
00:00:17,662 --> 00:00:21,329
Of course, we get here, and there's no arms deal in sight

7
00:00:21,437 --> 00:00:24,609
and instead, one of these toys starts attacking us.

8
00:00:27,360 --> 00:00:29,416
You look funny. What's the deal?

9
00:00:29,705 --> 00:00:32,291
I dunno. I have this feeling.

10
00:00:35,155 --> 00:00:35,884
Mugino!

11
00:00:39,692 --> 00:00:40,608
Thank you for that.

12
00:00:40,692 --> 00:00:42,611
Ultra happy to be of service.

13
00:00:45,431 --> 00:00:48,056
Geez, don't startle me like that, okay?

14
00:00:48,733 --> 00:00:49,858
Thank you, Mugin...

15
00:00:52,171 --> 00:00:52,639
Tch.

16
00:00:53,792 --> 00:00:56,787
I'd say those are adequate
enough results for a field test.

17
00:00:57,489 --> 00:00:59,614
We are steadily gathering data for the real thing.

18
00:00:59,650 --> 00:01:00,358
Aritomi.

19
00:01:00,386 --> 00:01:00,798
Huh?

20
00:01:10,318 --> 00:01:12,817
Oh, man. I've got a tummy ache!

21
00:01:12,900 --> 00:01:16,083
That was an exotic stew. I've never eaten turtle before.

22
00:01:16,163 --> 00:01:18,705
The beef Misaka brought was amazing, too.

23
00:01:18,937 --> 00:01:21,683
And because of that, I am now way too full!

24
00:01:21,775 --> 00:01:24,085
Maybe we should find some medicine for you.

25
00:01:27,040 --> 00:01:28,303
Oh, by the way.

26
00:01:29,060 --> 00:01:31,536
Did that talk you had with your teacher go all right?

27
00:01:31,900 --> 00:01:35,439
Yeah. It did. I think we found the perfect spot.

28
00:01:36,942 --> 00:01:38,003
You did, huh?

29
00:01:38,572 --> 00:01:40,037
Then it's almost time.

30
00:01:41,233 --> 00:01:41,818
Mm.

31
00:03:15,817 --> 00:03:16,393
So?

32
00:03:16,637 --> 00:03:18,211
Who's that you were talking to?

33
00:03:18,379 --> 00:03:18,760
Hm?

34
00:03:18,804 --> 00:03:20,663
That fine young man back there.

35
00:03:20,736 --> 00:03:22,209
Oh, just somebody I know.

36
00:03:22,241 --> 00:03:23,692
So evasive!

37
00:03:23,775 --> 00:03:25,988
Ooh! It was cookie boy, wasn't it?

38
00:03:26,608 --> 00:03:27,530
No, it wasn't!

39
00:03:27,617 --> 00:03:29,833
I swear, that's the last time I bake anything!

40
00:03:29,905 --> 00:03:31,197
Okay, fine,

41
00:03:31,233 --> 00:03:32,983
if that wasn't him, who is the cookie guy?

42
00:03:33,067 --> 00:03:34,526
I... I'm telling you he...

43
00:03:34,558 --> 00:03:35,522
Hello, Sissy.

44
00:03:35,844 --> 00:03:38,333
You're getting here late. What have you been up to?

45
00:03:38,358 --> 00:03:39,358
Ooh, I'll tell you.

46
00:03:39,442 --> 00:03:41,567
Ah! Hey, look, the elevator's here!

47
00:03:41,697 --> 00:03:44,769
Come on, come on, let's go! Quickly now, everybody! Heh.

48
00:03:45,748 --> 00:03:48,740
There she goes! So adorable!

49
00:03:50,650 --> 00:03:52,400
Congratulations, Edasaki.

50
00:03:52,683 --> 00:03:53,223
Huh?

51
00:03:53,900 --> 00:03:56,103
We hear you're being discharged. Right?

52
00:03:56,319 --> 00:03:59,669
Heh, yeah I am! I owe it all to you guys.

53
00:03:59,771 --> 00:04:03,161
Having that uniform waiting
for me really inspired me to work

54
00:04:03,185 --> 00:04:06,297
hard and finish my rehabilitation before summer was over!

55
00:04:09,692 --> 00:04:12,588
So, is everything set for when you get out of here?

56
00:04:12,788 --> 00:04:13,383
Mm-Hmm.

57
00:04:13,793 --> 00:04:16,729
Actually, Edasaki is going to be living with Haru'ue.

58
00:04:17,608 --> 00:04:18,477
Oh. Really?

59
00:04:18,983 --> 00:04:19,559
Yep.

60
00:04:19,712 --> 00:04:22,770
Well, you know. I've been in a home for so long.

61
00:04:23,333 --> 00:04:26,208
Suddenly living on her own would be really hard.

62
00:04:26,315 --> 00:04:28,732
I talked to my teachers about the situation,

63
00:04:28,948 --> 00:04:31,801
and they agreed that Banri and I could share a place.

64
00:04:33,025 --> 00:04:34,599
Oh, that's nice.

65
00:04:35,314 --> 00:04:37,424
So then, you'll be moving again, huh?

66
00:04:37,708 --> 00:04:39,833
We'd be happy to come by and help you guys out.

67
00:04:39,873 --> 00:04:41,527
That's okay, thanks though.

68
00:04:41,856 --> 00:04:44,231
Uiharu and I already took care of it.

69
00:04:44,275 --> 00:04:45,150
Seriously?

70
00:04:45,233 --> 00:04:45,651
Yep.

71
00:04:45,729 --> 00:04:48,707
We made a few calls and got
the movers lined up for tomorrow.

72
00:04:48,916 --> 00:04:50,242
Well, that was quick.

73
00:04:50,373 --> 00:04:52,148
